# WHY SO FEW FEDORA OEM PARTNERS vs UBUNTU?

# three structural reasons:
#
# 1. SUPPORT WINDOW MATH. ubuntu LTS gives OEMs a 5-year support
#    contract horizon to commit to drivers, certifications, and customer
#    support. fedora's 13-month support window would require
#    re-certification annually. ubuntu LTS is easier business.
