# 2. CANONICAL HAS A COMMERCIAL OEM PROGRAM. they actively pursue
#    OEM deals with paid support contracts. red hat focuses commercial
#    OEM work on RHEL (servers / workstations), not fedora — fedora
#    is positioned as upstream community work, not a commercial product.
