CLAUDE CODE — INSTALL ON FEDORA
-------------------------------

# anthropic's CLI agent. not in fedora repos. three install paths,
# ordered by simplicity. see also [[claude-code]] for the ptyxis
# shift+enter workaround.


# 1. NATIVE INSTALLER (recommended)
# self-contained binary. no Node.js dep, no system-wide JS toolchain.
# canonical URL is on claude.com/claude-code — check there if the
# script URL below has rotated:
curl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash
which claude && claude --version
