#   - NO MS OFFICE NATIVE. for casual work, LibreOffice or web 365
#     is fine. for heavy collab on .docx with track changes:
#     OnlyOffice has the best compatibility. or run office in a
#     VM (see VIRTUAL MACHINES).
#   - DIFFERENT FILE PATH CONVENTIONS. forward slashes, case-
